snippet.title: ULTROS – First Look Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Step into the surreal world of ULTROS and witness the psychedelic universe come to life in this first look at gameplay for the upcoming sci-fi adventure.

Assume the role of Ouji, a nimble sojourner and experience frenetic action combined with serene gardening gameplay with art from the mind of renowned artist El Huervo.

Coming to PS4, PS5 and PC in 2024, wishlist now!
PlayStation Store: https://store.playstation.com/concept/10003373/
Steam: https://bit.ly/3qSwEtQ 
Epic Games Store: https://store.epicgames.com/p/ultros
